                                <title type="desc" xml:lang="la">Summary of the canonization process of St Birgitta of Sweden</title>
                                <rubric xml:lang="la">Rubricacio seu summa tocius processus canonizacionis beate Brigide de Swecia</rubric>
                                <incipit>In nomine yhesu christi Misericordis et pii Ac eius Virginis matris et Beati Ieronimi Amen. QVia dominus noster papa et Collegium Cardinalium multis et arduis que in Romane curie alueum vndique confluunt quasi torrens</incipit>
                                <explicit>ixl dies accedentibus uero singulis infra octauas dei festi ad sepulchrum ipsum. xl. dies de iniuncta sibi penitencia misericorditer Relaxamus.</explicit>
                                <note>
                                    <p> The words <quote xml:lang="la">Rubricacio seu summa</quote> are repeated above the title on <locus from="1v" to="1v" scheme="folios"/> and parts of the words <quote xml:lang="la">beate brigide de</quote> are missing due to a tear in the leaf.</p>
                                    <p>
                                        <locusGrp>
                                            <locus from="1r" to="1r" scheme="folios"/>
                                            <locus from="22v" to="23v" scheme="folios"/>
                                        </locusGrp>: blank.</p>
                                </note>
                                <bibl>
                                    <title type="short" ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/bibl/107108">Collijn (1924–1931)</title>
                                    <citedRange from="571" to="607" unit="page"/>
                                </bibl>
                            </msItem>
                        </msContents>
