                                        <locus from="2r" to="2r" scheme="folios"/> In the rubric a plain initial <quote>I</quote> over 2 lines in black ink with a face in profile in the counterspace. Opening initial <quote>Q</quote> in black ink with simple leaf decoration in bows and counter space. <locusGrp>
