                                <textLang mainLang="la"/>
                                <title type="desc">Acts and proceedings from the canonization process of St Birgitta of Sweden</title>
                                <rubric>Acta et processus habitus coram Reuerendissimis in christo patribus dominis Gradensi Corphiensi et de zangro Cardinalibus Commissariis super negocio Canonizacionis Beate Brigide de Regno Swecie</rubric>
                                <incipit xml:lang="la">In nomine domini Amen Anno a natiuitate eiusdem Millesimo Tricentesimo Septuagesimo nono. Indiccione secunda die Iouis tercio mensis marcij ponit sanctissimi in christo patris et domini nostri domini vrbani diuina prouidencia pape sexti Anno primo. In mei notarii publici et testium infrascriptorum presencia discretus vir Nereus Nerey Cursor et magister Cursorum domini nostri pape</incipit>
                                <explicit xml:lang="la">vt predictorum copiam dicto sindico et procuratori et quibuscumque aliis eam petentibus et habere volentibus trademur predictorum petencium sumptibus et expensis.</explicit>
                                <finalRubric>Et sic est finis productorum.</finalRubric>
                                <note>
                                    <p> Below final rubric on <locus from="123r" to="123r" scheme="folios"/> is written: <quote xml:lang="la">Incipiunt attestaciones testium productorum et receptorum in Roma super sancto Canonizacionis pie memorie domine Brigide de Regno Swecie. Continuando folium sequens et cetera</quote>.</p>
                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="46v" to="46v" scheme="folios"/>: A note in the margin pointing out that three supplication letters are missing here but added at the end of the book, referring to the letters added on <locus from="250v" to="253r" scheme="folios"/>.</p>
                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="65r" to="79r" scheme="folios"/>: Miracles.</p>
                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="123v" to="123v" scheme="folios"/>: blank.</p>
                                </note>
                                <listBibl>
                                    <bibl>
                                        <title type="short" ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/bibl/107108">Collijn (1924–1931)</title>
                                        <citedRange from="3" to="244" unit="page"/>
                                    </bibl>
                                    <bibl>
                                        <title type="short" ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/bibl/107367">SRS 3</title>
                                        <citedRange from="2" to="2" unit="volume"/>
                                        <citedRange from="220" to="223" unit="page"/>
                                        <note>excerpt only</note>
                                    </bibl>
                                </listBibl>
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem class="test">
                                <locus from="124r" to="250v" scheme="folios"/>
                                <title type="uniform">Attestations from individual witnesses</title>
                                <rubric xml:lang="la">Incipiunt deposiciones testium productorum et receptorum in Roma Super articulis et miraculis pie memorie domine Beate Brigide de Regno Swecie ac Super negocio canonisacionis ipsius et cetera.</rubric>
                                <incipit defective="false">In christi nomine Amen sequuntur attestaciones testium productorum super vita conuersacione et miraculis recolende memorie domine Brigide</incipit>
                                <explicit defective="false">Cetera vero signa et sigilla dictis scripturis appensa et consignata dixit ipse testis illis sibi exhibitis non cognoscere.</explicit>
                                <finalRubric>Et sic sit finis huiusmodi processus et cetera. laus christo et gloria per seculorum secula Amen. </finalRubric>
                                <listBibl>
                                    <bibl>
                                        <title type="short" ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/bibl/107108">Collijn (1924–1931)</title>
                                        <citedRange from="245" to="570" unit="page"/>
                                    </bibl>
                                    <bibl>
                                        <title type="short" ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/bibl/107367">SRS 3</title>
                                        <citedRange from="2" to="2" unit="volume"/>
                                        <citedRange from="223" to="230" unit="page"/>
                                        <note>excerpts only</note>
                                    </bibl>
                                </listBibl>
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem>
                                <locus from="250v" to="253r" scheme="folios"/>
                                <textLang mainLang="la"/>
                                <title type="desc" xml:lang="la">Supplication letters for the canonization process of St Birgitta</title>
                                <rubric xml:lang="la">littere supplicatorie pro Canonizacione beate Brigide. </rubric>
                                <incipit defective="false">Hic sequuntur tres littere Supplicatorie directe domino vrbano pape vi pro Canonizacione beate Brigide de quibus fit mencio supra folio xxiijj in margine hoc est Cxiiii. Sanctissimo in christo patri ac domino domino suo Carissimo domino vrbano</incipit>
                                <explicit defective="false">sic eciam ad placandam diuine maiestatis offensam suis sanctis precibus esse dignetur patrona misericors et favorabilis advocata. Datum Orabro Strengianensis diocesis Anno ab incarnacione Millesimo CCC Septuagesimo nono xviii die mensis Ianuarii sub Sigillis nostris.</explicit>
                                <note>
                                    <p>The words <quote xml:lang="la">hoc est Cxiiii</quote> on <locus from="250v" to="250v" scheme="folios"/> are an addition to the incipit by another hand, after which a space of ca four lines has been left blank. Below last line of the explicit on <locus from="253r" to="253r" scheme="folios"/> the phrase <quote xml:lang="la">hoc est die prisce virginis</quote> is added.</p>
                                    <p>On <locus from="253v" to="253v" scheme="folios"/>
                                        <quote>processus canonizacionis beate brigide de Swecia</quote> is written in the same style as on <locus from="1v" to="1v" scheme="folios"/>.</p>
                                </note>
                                <bibl>
                                    <title type="short" ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/bibl/107108">Collijn (1924–1931)</title>
                                    <citedRange from="55" to="61" unit="page"/>
                                </bibl>
